**Topic check:** Vectors. The tag is correct.

**Solution**

\[
\overrightarrow{AB}=\begin{pmatrix}5\\3\end{pmatrix}
\]

and

\[
\overrightarrow{CB}=\begin{pmatrix}-2\\4\end{pmatrix}
\]

So

\[
\overrightarrow{BC}=-\overrightarrow{CB}
=\begin{pmatrix}2\\-4\end{pmatrix}
\]

\[
\overrightarrow{AC}
=\overrightarrow{AB}+\overrightarrow{BC}
=\begin{pmatrix}5\\3\end{pmatrix}
+\begin{pmatrix}2\\-4\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}7\\-1\end{pmatrix}
\]

**Answer:** \(\begin{pmatrix}7\\-1\end{pmatrix}\).
